{"tid":1634183,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"馬蹄露旺角遭「私了」變紅豆沙 商台DJ阿檸爆粗斥：濕X藍絲","createTime":"2019-10-07T06:52:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T11:36:08.000Z","uid":130626,"like":54,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c05242fd04688d6b88a9569aa759cbeaf3c2f536","tid":1634183,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:52:05.000Z","msg":"有見各區都有示威活動，警方昨日都短訊呼籲巿民不要外出，但撐警的51歲馬蹄露昨日卻到高危的旺角，有指她現場涉影抗爭者時，被搶去手機，雙方起爭執，馬蹄露遭「私了」，她發狂起飛腳踢黑衣人，隨即被推跌在地上，她遇襲後嘴角及頭部受傷，現場有一名外籍記者陪同她到旺角警署報案。<br />\n<br />\n馬蹄露嘴角流血，網民揶揄她變了「紅豆沙」，有網民力斥她先撩是鬥非，連阮民安(Tommy)昨看過網上流出片段都在facebook鬧爆馬蹄露行為，他留言：「馬蹄露？OkOk！無端端有人埋嚟影X你大頭，你都X9佢啦！你無端端走去影人做乜X啫，之後仲要起飛腳踢人，拍真情咩，onXX咁！唉...人一藍...BTW 個下巴...」網民即留言和應：「佢白癡到咁。」阮民安也答：「藍絲係咁上下啦。」<br />\n<br />\n商台DJ阿檸（薛晉寧）也在fb轉貼馬蹄露遭「私了」真相新聞，相中有她起腳踢黑衣人，他留言：「唔關職業事，你只係一個濕X藍絲，同全世界嘅自私精一X樣。」向來愛抽水的林作都出來「靚抽」，他轉發了馬蹄露被襲新聞後自嘲：「樣衰都係一種罪，我講我。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191007/large/1570427058_cb35.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191007%2Flarge%2F1570427058_cb35.jpg&h=f339d68e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191007/60126267\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191007%2F60126267&d=fuRTyfFj%2BaUlIJflnhZSn8%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=bc3c57a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191007%2F60126267&h=b3457c0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191007/60126267</a>"},{"pid":"43d3a048bf7d70bf21f688ae987fa3044abc90cf","tid":1634183,"uid":76632,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:59:26.000Z","msg":"樣衰唔係罪，缺乏內在美先係罪。<br />\n<br />\n相由心生，佢點整容都係咁樣衰。"},{"pid":"9a2acc28cf2300e2ee06b75547a4fcf363d86657","tid":1634183,"uid":248571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:12:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0704b069714253d7586872ed2aaf6b687734f4f9","tid":1634183,"uid":190789,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:15:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />毒檸王國成日聽"},{"pid":"d66a266ad21216a560f394d1d9d0e6f8d01f222c","tid":1634183,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43d3a048bf7d70bf21f688ae987fa3044abc90cf","tid":1634183,"uid":76632,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:59:26.000Z","msg":"樣衰唔係罪，缺乏內在美先係罪。<br />\n<br />\n相由心生，佢點整容都係咁樣衰。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:59:28.000Z","msg":"其實唔止樣，佢果隻乞人憎既氣質隔住個mon都feel到"},{"pid":"7ff282cca3a40413e8c6fce9430e98be9b8e873b","tid":1634183,"uid":311907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:59:52.000Z","msg":"再講多次 文宣係要主動出擊<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634763\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634763</a>"},{"pid":"644205be7143e71fd4a237ea4ef128c801511c58","tid":1634183,"uid":323797,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:00:02.000Z","msg":"新口號：和勇相連 永不割蓆！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634504\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634504</a><br />\n<br />\n各位巴打絲打幫幫手討論下要唔要新口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7iSSOZK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7iSSOZK.jpg&h=4440f0bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"27391446efebc3bb2bcc29d57310a40706209382","tid":1634183,"uid":19437,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:00:42.000Z","msg":"恨做女一恨到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c960be554f8dc21ef22e95e7398cfc1de31c23f","tid":1634183,"uid":23635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11: